WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )


00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Brother Su Yang.

00:01:05.319 --> 00:01:06.239
Brother Su Yang.

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:08.920
Brother Su Yang!

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:14.719
What's wrong?

00:01:14.719 --> 00:01:15.959
Is it another headache?

00:01:15.959 --> 00:01:17.319
Why are you sweating so much?

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:22.480
I'm fine.

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:23.840
Come on.

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:24.760
Let's go grab some good food.

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:26.159
Okay, let's hurry.

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:27.400
Let's go.

00:01:41.599 --> 00:01:42.840
Weren't there supposed to be five people?

00:01:43.760 --> 00:01:45.040
Where are the other two?

00:01:46.879 --> 00:01:47.920
One couldn't be bothered to come.

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.879
The other one's missing.

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:54.000
Missing?

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:58.280
A while back, I dumped him on Black Street.

00:01:58.680 --> 00:01:59.840
Then I lost contact with him.

00:02:00.319 --> 00:02:02.719
If he hadn't texted me at some point

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:04.120
saying he was in secret training,

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:05.239
I'd almost suspect

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:06.640
he'd already died on Black Street.

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:08.479
And the other one?

00:02:09.240 --> 00:02:10.199
The other one

00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:11.159
is from Black Street.

00:02:11.439 --> 00:02:12.280
His name is Su Yang.

00:02:12.719 --> 00:02:13.759
Supposedly, he knows you.

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:19.360
You even got him to come out?

00:02:20.479 --> 00:02:21.919
So you really do know him?

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:27.560
This kiddo of mine

00:02:28.879 --> 00:02:31.080
is quite an interesting guy.

00:02:31.719 --> 00:02:33.520
Kiddo?

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:35.479
Yeah.

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:38.159
Didn't you ask me before

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:39.639
whether the underworlds of other main cities

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:42.199
are all in chaos,

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:44.319
full of powerful experts?

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:48.360
Doesn't Shanhai City have any?

00:02:50.240 --> 00:02:51.719
Let me put it this way.

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:54.800
Back then, the scum on Black Street,

00:02:55.199 --> 00:02:56.039
Little Madman

00:02:56.039 --> 00:02:56.919
killed half of them.

00:02:57.439 --> 00:02:59.000
As for the other half,

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:04.719
I killed them.

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:09.879
I mean, all that mess back then

00:03:09.879 --> 00:03:11.840
was seriously messing up my gaming time.

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:14.000
So I had a flash of inspiration

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.639
and just eliminated the source of the problem.

00:03:16.919 --> 00:03:18.560
After that, no one ever bothered me again.

00:03:20.599 --> 00:03:21.240
So...

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:24.000
that's how Black Street came to be?

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:28.560
Black Street back in the day

00:03:29.719 --> 00:03:32.120
was truly full of all sorts of lowlifes.

00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:34.360
Nothing like it is now.

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:36.719
The people living there

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:39.800
were genuinely wicked and evil.

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:43.360
Until Su Yang and I wiped them all out.

00:03:43.960 --> 00:03:45.879
Then Black Street's fame grew,

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.240
and that's what drew in

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.800
all those experts who came to live in seclusion.

00:03:50.199 --> 00:03:51.960
That's how today's

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:55.159
core district of Black Street came about.

00:03:58.159 --> 00:03:59.840
That's all in the past.

00:03:59.919 --> 00:04:01.039
Let's drop it. Let's drop it.

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:02.879
What about the rest of you?

00:04:04.639 --> 00:04:05.319
Hello, sir.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:06.960
My name is Liu Xiaorou.

00:04:07.159 --> 00:04:08.759
My Divine Blessing is the Pig.

00:04:09.199 --> 00:04:11.199
I... I'm kind of a coward.

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:12.280
Afraid of pain.

00:04:12.759 --> 00:04:14.000
My combat ability is extremely weak.

00:04:14.639 --> 00:04:16.839
But I'm not exactly stupid either.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.759
Sorry for the trouble, everyone.

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:23.279
So you're the Grand Elder's grandson.

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:30.759
Now this is interesting.

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:34.120
I know.

00:04:34.439 --> 00:04:35.680
Grandpa wasted a precious spot

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:37.839
just to gild my resume.

00:04:38.279 --> 00:04:39.519
But on the road ahead,

00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:41.000
I'll do my best

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:42.439
to help everyone in other areas.

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:46.839
Yu Shuai, blessed by Chen Xiang.

00:04:48.319 --> 00:04:48.959
And me,

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:50.319
blessed by Zhu Rong.

00:04:53.279 --> 00:04:53.959
No, no, no.

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:55.480
Is Shanhai City out of people?

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:58.000
How did even she make the team?

00:04:58.959 --> 00:05:01.399
You have no idea how strong she is.

00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:04.399
Even stronger than people on Black Street.

00:05:04.399 --> 00:05:05.079
Nah, not a chance.

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:06.480
That's impossible.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:12.800
What are you doing?

00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:16.040
You guys keep chatting.

00:05:16.040 --> 00:05:17.079
I've got something to take care of.

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:19.160
I haven't spoken yet.

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:22.720
Hey cutie, I'm coming! Bye!

00:05:27.959 --> 00:05:28.879
Um...

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:32.319
So...

00:05:33.160 --> 00:05:34.319
Let me say a few words.

00:05:35.959 --> 00:05:37.839
How much do you know about Divine Blessing?

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:40.839
Not much.

00:05:42.519 --> 00:05:43.439
Recently,

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:46.680
I had experts research ancient texts

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:47.560
and unofficial histories.

00:05:48.079 --> 00:05:49.959
We came to some conclusions.

00:05:50.199 --> 00:05:51.399
At every critical point,

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.120
an Immortal Descent will occur.

00:05:53.519 --> 00:05:55.360
Just like the one a month ago.

00:05:55.639 --> 00:05:56.600
During the Immortal Descent,

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:59.160
the bond between the blessed and the immortal strengthens,

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:03.240
boosting their compatibility,

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.600
which causes the blessed one's power

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:06.920
to skyrocket.

00:06:07.560 --> 00:06:09.959
Based on our rigorous calculations,

00:06:10.439 --> 00:06:12.720
for every 5% increase in compatibility,

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:15.639
you gain one extra ability from the immortal.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.240
If compatibility reaches 100%,

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:20.240
you gain everything the immortal has.

00:06:21.279 --> 00:06:22.199
Any questions?

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:23.920
Speak.

00:06:25.199 --> 00:06:26.160
I didn't understand.

00:06:26.480 --> 00:06:27.439
Fine.

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.759
You two didn't get it either, did you?

00:06:31.319 --> 00:06:32.360
Meeting adjourned. Meeting adjourned.

00:06:32.360 --> 00:06:33.480
Everyone out, out, out.

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:35.079
Oh, right.

00:06:37.240 --> 00:06:40.120
Sky City just urgently developed a device

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:42.160
that can measure compatibility.

00:06:42.399 --> 00:06:44.040
This week, I'll schedule a time

00:06:44.079 --> 00:06:45.720
for everyone to get tested.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.639
We depart in one week.

00:06:48.399 --> 00:06:49.560
Meeting dismissed.

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:51.879
Scram.

00:07:00.199 --> 00:07:02.680
Wonder if that idiot Xu Siguo

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:06.040
can make it back within a week.

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:07.680
Not bad.

00:07:08.439 --> 00:07:09.639
Starting today,

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:12.000
you've officially graduated.

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:13.639
Remember,

00:07:13.879 --> 00:07:16.600
don't go around dropping my name.

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:19.240
You and I have no connection.

00:07:19.519 --> 00:07:20.800
If you get into trouble later,

00:07:21.279 --> 00:07:23.000
don't come running to me.

00:07:23.439 --> 00:07:24.279
And especially,

00:07:24.839 --> 00:07:27.279
don't contact your three senior brothers.

00:07:35.319 --> 00:07:36.720
The previous three senior brothers,

00:07:37.399 --> 00:07:38.879
Master openly acknowledged them.

00:07:39.480 --> 00:07:40.959
Why is it that with me,

00:07:41.959 --> 00:07:43.319
he forbids it from being known?

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.519
A clean break.

00:07:48.839 --> 00:07:50.000
Straight to retirement.

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:54.360
I understand.

00:07:54.959 --> 00:07:55.720
Legend has it

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:57.600
when Sun Wukong studied under

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.839
Patriarch Subodhi,

00:07:59.240 --> 00:08:00.519
he was also forbidden to reveal it.

00:08:00.959 --> 00:08:02.079
After Master finished speaking,

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.519
he turned away at the last moment.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:06.399
That means everything he said was the opposite.

00:08:09.399 --> 00:08:10.199
I must work hard

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:11.560
to glorify the sect,

00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:13.680
stick close to my senior brothers,

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:15.160
and strive to surpass them.

00:08:32.519 --> 00:08:34.080
Xu Siguo, reporting back!

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:45.759
You...

00:08:46.279 --> 00:08:47.679
aren't you socially anxious?

00:08:47.879 --> 00:08:48.639
Master said,

00:08:49.159 --> 00:08:51.120
a young man should forge ahead boldly.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.440
My name is Siguo, "reflect on faults,"

00:08:52.759 --> 00:08:54.759
which means making others kneel before me

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:57.200
and reflect on the faults they've committed.

00:08:59.240 --> 00:09:00.200
He's lost his mind.

00:09:02.159 --> 00:09:03.159
Seems like it.

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:06.919
Forget it.

00:09:07.159 --> 00:09:09.159
Let me take you to the training ground first.

00:09:16.360 --> 00:09:17.440
Forge ahead boldly.

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:24.000
Everyone.

00:09:24.559 --> 00:09:28.960
This is Sky City's newest invention,

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:31.720
a machine that tests compatibility levels.

00:09:32.159 --> 00:09:33.919
Just place your hand on it,

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:35.279
and the machine will measure

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:37.919
the density of immortal energy within you,

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:40.360
to determine your compatibility level.

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:43.120
Who wants to try first?

00:09:44.679 --> 00:09:45.559
Over here!

00:09:45.919 --> 00:09:47.080
I'm the weakest one.

00:09:47.519 --> 00:09:48.720
Let me try first for everyone.

00:09:49.879 --> 00:09:50.799
Quite humble.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:52.240
Come on.

00:09:55.759 --> 00:09:57.559
Zero point five.

00:10:07.759 --> 00:10:08.799
Really not strong at all.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:10.720
Go back. Stop grinning like a fool.

00:10:12.840 --> 00:10:13.799
Who's next?

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:22.000
One point five.

00:10:24.679 --> 00:10:25.480
I'll go then.

00:10:25.879 --> 00:10:26.679
Alright.

00:10:34.120 --> 00:10:35.840
One point nine.

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:36.799
Not bad.

00:10:37.039 --> 00:10:38.720
Not bad at all!

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.279
Quite pleased with yourself.

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:46.080
Two point zero.

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:01.200
I'm really curious what this Madman will score.

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:03.879
Su Yang.

00:11:04.519 --> 00:11:05.480
You're just in time.

00:11:05.919 --> 00:11:06.840
This machine

00:11:06.879 --> 00:11:08.279
is the newest invention,

00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:10.120
designed to test compatibility levels.

00:11:10.120 --> 00:11:11.279
Give it a try. Come on, come on.

00:11:11.279 --> 00:11:12.240
What a hassle.

00:11:13.399 --> 00:11:15.440
Those old folks want to see it.

00:11:15.679 --> 00:11:16.759
I don't want to either.

00:11:16.879 --> 00:11:17.519
Help me out.

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:18.639
Help me out, please.

00:11:20.159 --> 00:11:21.080
Hello, senior brother.

00:11:23.159 --> 00:11:25.720
Junior brother Xu Siguo seeks your guidance.

00:11:27.919 --> 00:11:28.799
Junior brother.

00:11:31.039 --> 00:11:32.360
Your current strength

00:11:32.799 --> 00:11:34.679
far surpasses mine.

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:37.679
A young man should be sharp and bold.

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:39.759
You have the bearing of an unbeatable warrior.

00:11:39.960 --> 00:11:41.559
You should walk the path of invincibility,

00:11:41.679 --> 00:11:43.960
and defeat every prodigy in this world.

00:11:45.399 --> 00:11:46.960
Cast aside your fear.

00:11:47.159 --> 00:11:48.320
Cast aside your cowardice.

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:50.559
From this day forward,

00:11:50.799 --> 00:11:52.080
for a thousand years to come,

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:53.919
they'll remember your name.

00:11:54.840 --> 00:11:56.320
Xu Siguo.

00:12:00.679 --> 00:12:02.960
Is this guy out of his mind?

00:12:03.799 --> 00:12:07.159
Back then, no one in the village survived but me.

00:12:08.399 --> 00:12:09.120
Pardon my poor display.

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:10.679
Yang Jian!

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:11.639
Manifest!

00:12:22.679 --> 00:12:23.720
Manifest!

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:25.759
I should have it too, right?

00:12:26.519 --> 00:12:27.200
Let me try.

00:12:27.960 --> 00:12:28.879
Manifest!

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:36.000
Oh no.

00:12:36.559 --> 00:12:38.200
I forgot to shout the name.

00:12:47.679 --> 00:12:48.480
That was close.

00:12:49.240 --> 00:12:51.000
Two more seconds and I'd have exploded.

00:12:52.200 --> 00:12:53.519
Next time, remember to shout the name.

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.559
Otherwise, all kinds of weird stuff

00:12:55.960 --> 00:12:56.879
will come pouring out.

00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:10.600
Data error.

00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:16.960
Try again.

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:21.360
Error. Data error.

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:24.080
Try again.

00:13:25.799 --> 00:13:27.039
Error, error, error.

00:13:27.320 --> 00:13:28.679
Error. Error.

00:13:28.799 --> 00:13:29.399
That's enough.

00:13:29.399 --> 00:13:31.720
That latest piece of tech...

00:13:31.840 --> 00:13:33.200
The data's bound to be off.

00:13:33.639 --> 00:13:34.759
Forget it. None of it matters now.

00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:35.879
It doesn't matter.

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:38.639
By the way,

00:13:39.720 --> 00:13:40.759
when are we heading out?

00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:41.960
In a week.

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:44.320
Then me and Little Cleaner will head out first.

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:47.759
Aren't we all flying together?

00:13:48.120 --> 00:13:49.080
Don't you think

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:51.039
that Little Cleaner and I,

00:13:51.159 --> 00:13:52.320
riding together in a carriage,

00:13:52.600 --> 00:13:53.320
seeing the mountains,

00:13:53.480 --> 00:13:54.159
seeing the rivers,

00:13:54.559 --> 00:13:55.440
seeing the fields of flowers,

00:13:56.080 --> 00:13:57.360
sounds like a really nice time?

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:00.080
But what if on the way,

00:14:00.120 --> 00:14:01.720
you run into an assassination attempt?

00:14:02.120 --> 00:14:02.879
I...

00:14:09.519 --> 00:14:10.759
What kind of carriage do you want?

00:14:12.320 --> 00:14:13.000
Just...

00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:15.519
the kind pulled by horses.

00:14:16.279 --> 00:14:16.960
Don't worry.

00:14:17.240 --> 00:14:18.960
I'll have it delivered

00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:20.519
to your clinic's doorstep ASAP.

00:14:21.519 --> 00:14:22.559
See you in the Imperial Capital.

00:14:22.639 --> 00:14:23.240
Thanks.

00:14:23.559 --> 00:14:24.200
Little Feng,

00:14:24.480 --> 00:14:25.720
I'm really rooting for you.

00:14:43.879 --> 00:14:46.039
The moment Su Yang made his move,

00:14:46.039 --> 00:14:46.960
did you see it?

00:14:48.600 --> 00:14:50.320
Xu Siguo went flying through the air, whoosh!

00:14:50.320 --> 00:14:52.480
I mean Su Yang! Su Yang!

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:56.279
I didn't dare look.

00:14:56.440 --> 00:14:57.240
I saw it.

00:14:57.879 --> 00:14:59.679
The instant he struck,

00:14:59.919 --> 00:15:02.120
several divine figures appeared behind him.

00:15:02.679 --> 00:15:03.720
Though they weren't clear,

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:05.919
they were definitely real.

00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:09.200
You didn't get any of that, did you?

00:15:12.919 --> 00:15:13.679
Right now,

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:15.960
hurry up and get him to the hospital.

00:15:17.279 --> 00:15:18.279
I want to ask,

00:15:18.480 --> 00:15:20.720
did he trade his brain for that little bit of power?

00:15:21.759 --> 00:15:23.360
He used to just be a bit naive.

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:25.039
Now he's definitely an idiot.

00:15:25.279 --> 00:15:26.159
Get him out of my sight, fast.

00:15:26.240 --> 00:15:26.759
Hurry!

00:15:26.919 --> 00:15:27.600
Okay.